          .layui-form-item
            label.layui-form-label(for='phone')
              span.x-red *
              | 手机
            .layui-input-inline
              input#phone.layui-input(type='text', name='phone', required='', lay-verify='phone', autocomplete='off')
            .layui-form-mid.layui-word-aux
              span.x-red *
              | 将会成为您唯一的登入名
          .layui-form-item
            label.layui-form-label(for='L_email')
